<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.8">
<l>calamā mukilpal kaṇappōrk kaḷattuc</l>
<l rend="indent">caramā ripoḻin teṅkumpū caliṭṭu</l>
<l>nalivā ṉuṟakkēṭa kamkōppa vaṉpōl</l>
<l rend="indent">nārā yaṇaṉmuṉ mukamkāt tamalai</l>
<l>yilaivēy kurampait tavamā muṉiva</l>
<l rend="indent">riruntār naṭuvē ceṉṟaṇār coṟiya</l>
<l>kolaivāyc ciṉavēṅ kaikaḷniṉ ṟuṟaṅkum</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉumkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that Nārāyaṇa [used to] protect the vanguard</l>
<l rend="indent">as if graspping a shield,</l>
<l rend="indent">when a multitude of massive rain clouds [came],</l>
<l rend="indent">pouring down arrow[-like] rain all over the battle field</l>
<l rend="indent">[as] the war raged, creating havoc,</l>
<l>called Govardhana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where angry tigers with murderous mouths,</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone inside huts of leaves and bamboo</l>
<l rend="indent">as sages great with tapas sit scratching their necks</l>
<l rend="indent">while they remain sleeping,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
